Bradley 創立，可以觀看他介紹此系統的 Youtube 影片「"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d93SGaf82OM&list=PLAl0gPKnL3V8s7dPXoo07mYnuErhWVk8b","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Intro & Overview of Pillars, Pipelines & Vaults – Notion Life Operating System"}]},{"type":"text","value":"」。這個系統的目標是能每天都能聚焦在要做的事上面（Focus），且持續與目標或期望的自己對齊、持續推薦（Alignment），並將這些經驗與持續獲得的知識建立一個讓我們能取用的知識庫（Knowledge）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PPV 系統架構如其名，分別是："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pillars（支柱）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pipelines（行動渠道）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vaults（知識庫)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三者的關係如下圖（截自  August Bradley 的 Youtube）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"image-20230621-012820.png","src":"/attachments/image-20230621-012820.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在人生中，總有幾個面向是想持續推進的，這些面向就像是一個個支柱（Pillar），撐著我們往期望的未來與想成為的模樣前進，像是個人成長（Growth）、家庭與生活（Home/Life）、事業（Business）等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"支柱（Pillar）將人生分成好幾個區塊，每個支柱又分為不斷推進的行動渠道（Pipeline）以及與其相關的知識庫（Vault)，這兩者會持續的交互，在行動下累積知識，在拓展的知識下做出更好的決策與行動，並且透過定期檢視（Cycles）確保我們是持續往目標前進的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每個 Pillar 的 Pipeline 又分為以下幾類的資料庫："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有價值的目標（Value Goals）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目標的關鍵成效（Goal Outcomes）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"專案（Projects）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行動事項（Action Items / Tasks）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其 Vault 則分為："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多媒體知識庫（Media Vault）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"課程與培訓知識庫（Courses & Training Vault）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"筆記與靈感知識庫（Notes & Ideas Vault）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工具與技巧知識庫（Tools & Skill Vault）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Pipeline 部分，會先在有價值的目標（Value Goals）中，透過自己在這個支柱中想要達到的成就、成為的形象、期望看到的景象去設定目標。這些目標通常是抽象的，於是要藉由 SMART 原則訂定目標的關鍵成效（Goal Outcomes），當達到這個成效時，也就代表目標是達成的。接著就可以思考可以做什麼事情，讓現況更接近關鍵成效，這些事情就會是一個個專案（Projects），其中則是一個個的行動事項（Action Items）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這個概念其實在產品開發很常見，每個產品都會有個 Vission 與 Mission，然後會訂定每年想要達到的關鍵指標，為了達到這些指標會訂出策略，然後每個策略都會有要做的事情。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Vault 的部分，我想每個人有自己習慣的知識管理架構，倒不一定限定這樣分類。但對於這樣的分類，我倒是有些觀點：多媒體知識庫能提升廣度、課程與培訓知識庫則是增加深度、筆記與靈感是自己的沈澱、工具與技巧則是在這個 Pillar 中的磨刀石（斧頭與砍樹的故事）。"}]}]},"title_en":"PPV Life Operating System","slug":"ppv-life-operation-system","aliases":["PPV 人生經營系統","PPV Life Operating System"],"created_at":"2023-06-13T03:17:52.000Z","updated_at":"2023-06-20T18:00:48.000Z","published_at":"2023-06-20T18:00:43.000Z","tags":["knowledge"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"dev-only-content","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"main-vault :: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"obsidian://open?vault=Main&file=5.%20Area%20of%20Responsibility%2F%F0%9F%93%96%20%E5%A